* text=auto

*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf
*.vbs text eol=crlf

*.sh text eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary

# Exclude diagnostic and bug-investigation files from the GitHub source
# archive zip. v0.2.0 security review (see CHANGELOG) recommended that
# probe/ POC scripts not ship to end users; they use fixed ports for
# one-shot manual diagnostics, not the production dynamic-port path.
# Developers cloning the repo via git still get these directories.
probe/ export-ignore
docs/bugs/ export-ignore
